<h1>Topics in Field Theory</h1>

<h2>August - November '14</h2>

<p>This seminar will discuss assorted topics in field theory. The choice of topics is eclectic and idiosyncratic, largely reflecting the interests of the participants.</p>

<p>Each meeting will go on for an hour and a half. We meet every Saturday at 2:00 pm in Hall 123.</p>

<p>Note: The symbol "<b>*</b>" next to a reference means it was mentioned in passing and is only tangentially related to the material discussed in the talk.</p>

